org.scilab.modules.graphic_objects
Class MainDataLoader

java.lang.Object
  org.scilab.modules.graphic_objects.MainDataLoader

public class MainDataLoader
extends java.lang.Object

Class MainDataLoader A utility class used to switch to the appropriate data loading class depending on the type of the object whose data is loaded. A class is used for purely Java-based objects and another one is used to load the data of data model (i.e. C++-based) objects.
